==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Peise
<hw>Peise</hw>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <def>To poise or weigh.</def>
<mark>[Obs.]</mark> <rj><au>Chaucer.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Lest leaden slumber <qex>peise</qex> me down.</q>
<rj><qau>Shak.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Peitrel</ent>⟦br⟧
